The South African Broadcasting Corporation (SABC) news will on Sunday rebroadcast the historic debate between the African National Congress’s Nelson Mandela and the National Party’s FW de Klerk. The debate took place in 14 April, in the run-up to the 1994 elections. You can watch the debate on the SABC News Channel 404. The debate will also be lived streamed and available on the SABC News app as well as Facebook. Click link below for more on the story: